<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 06:18:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国通过消费刺激措施走出了一条不走寻常路的道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fridges-not-bridges-china-veers-off-beaten-path-with-consumer-stimulus-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国利用超长期国债为消费品以旧换新计划提供资金，这背离了通常通过增加投资来支持经济的做法，并引发了人们对针对家庭需求采取更多刺激措施的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fridges-not-bridges-china-veers-off-beaten-path-with-consumer-stimulus-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业寻求削减印尼新建镍冶炼厂的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-seek-cut-stakes-new-indonesian-nickel-smelters-2024-07-26/</link><description>一位印度尼西亚官员周五表示，中国公司正在与潜在投资者进行谈判，以减少其在印度尼西亚镍冶炼厂的股份，以使其产品有资格获得美国电动汽车税收抵免。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-seek-cut-stakes-new-indonesian-nickel-smelters-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”袭击台湾、淹没菲律宾后袭击中国东南部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/typhoon-gaemi-lashes-southeast-china-after-pounding-taiwan-flooding-philippines-2024-07-26/</link><description>台风“盖美”周五袭击了中国沿海福建省的城镇，带来大雨和强风，这是今年袭击中国的最强风暴，开始向人口稠密的内陆地区移动，受到广泛关注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/typhoon-gaemi-lashes-southeast-china-after-pounding-taiwan-flooding-philippines-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国降息序列暗示MLF作用减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rate-cuts-sequence-hints-reduced-role-mlf-2024-07-26/</link><description>分析师表示，中国最新的一系列降息表明央行的货币框架已经发生变化，短期回购利率成为主要信号，中期借贷便利（MLF）的作用减弱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rate-cuts-sequence-hints-reduced-role-mlf-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>韩国估计，朝鲜经济在经历多年萎缩后，将于 2023 年实现飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/north-koreas-economy-surged-2023-after-years-contraction-south-estimates-2024-07-26/</link><description>据韩国央行估计，随着 COVID-19 大流行边境管制放松后与中国的贸易增加，朝鲜经济在连续三年萎缩后，于 2023 年大幅增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/north-koreas-economy-surged-2023-after-years-contraction-south-estimates-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>科学家表示，气候变化导致降雨量变化更大、台风更猛烈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/climate-change-causing-more-change-rainfall-fiercer-typhoons-scientists-say-2024-07-26/</link><description>科学家在周五发表的一篇论文中表示，气候变化正在推动世界各地降雨模式的变化，这也可能加剧台风和其他热带风暴。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:48:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/climate-change-causing-more-change-rainfall-fiercer-typhoons-scientists-say-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部长王毅承诺与俄罗斯共同致力于东亚和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-foreign-minister-wang-pledges-work-with-russia-east-asian-peace-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国外长王毅表示，在国际动荡中，中俄应就东亚合作保持沟通协调，促进地区和平稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-foreign-minister-wang-pledges-work-with-russia-east-asian-peace-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着疯狂的一周结束，日元稳定，亚洲股市疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-26/</link><description>周五，日元兑美元汇率稳定在 12 周高点附近，而亚太股市在经历 4 月中旬以来最糟糕的交易日后一天仍处于弱势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:45:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着套利交易的平仓，日元将创三个月来最强劲的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-heads-strongest-week-3-months-carry-trades-unwind-2024-07-26/</link><description>周五，日元有望迎来近三个月来最强劲的一周，因为交易员在重要的美国通胀数据可能巩固降息预期之前解除了长期做空日元的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 01:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-heads-strongest-week-3-months-carry-trades-unwind-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>美军寻求战略优势，在中国紧张局势中建立澳大利亚北部基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-seeking-strategic-advantages-builds-up-australias-northern-bases-2024-07-26/</link><description>路透社对文件的审查以及对美国和澳大利亚国防官员的采访显示，美国军方正在澳大利亚北部建设基础设施，以帮助其在与中国爆发危机时向南海投射力量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 01:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-seeking-strategic-advantages-builds-up-australias-northern-bases-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>王毅：中印应相向而行，关系具有重要影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-india-should-work-same-direction-relations-have-an-important-impact-says-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅表示，希望中印双方相向而行，探讨周边国家相处之道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 23:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-india-should-work-same-direction-relations-have-an-important-impact-says-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>印度和中国同意紧急处理边界问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-china-agree-approach-border-issues-with-urgency-2024-07-25/</link><description>印度外长苏杰生周四在老挝会见了中国外长王毅，两国领导人同意尽快解决边界问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-china-agree-approach-border-issues-with-urgency-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国宝钢将在沙特的钢板投资增至10亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-baosteel-boost-investment-steel-plate-saudi-1-billion-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国最大的上市钢铁制造商宝山钢铁股份有限公司（宝钢）周四表示，将把对沙特阿拉伯一家钢板合资企业的投资从之前的约 4.375 亿美元增加一倍多，达到 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-baosteel-boost-investment-steel-plate-saudi-1-billion-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰要求香港不要让俄罗斯规避制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</link><description>乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库莱巴周四访问香港，并呼吁其领导人李约翰阻止俄罗斯利用香港作为规避西方因莫斯科全面乌克兰战争而对其实施制裁的手段。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 13:23:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，华为销量激增，苹果中国智能手机出货量下降6.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-china-smartphone-shipments-leap-while-apple-share-dips-2024-07-25/</link><description>市场研究公司 Canalys 的数据显示，由于苹果面临来自华为 (HWT.UL) 等竞争对手的激烈竞争，2024 年第二季度苹果在中国的智能手机出货量下降了 6.7%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-china-smartphone-shipments-leap-while-apple-share-dips-2024-07-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>